# GTEx SETBP1 decoupleR inputs: 

## TF regulation prior: CollecTRI (human)
* The prior network for [decoupleR](https://saezlab.github.io/decoupleR/) was constructed using [CollecTRI](https://github.com/saezlab/CollecTRI) for human on 230525. The file is located in this github repository as `human_prior_tri.csv`


## Expression prior: GTEx expression data (tpm)
* 31 different tissues from human GTEx data, normalized by tpm. 
* input array was already constructed in PANDA network construction and is titled `GTEx_exp_files_array.txt`
